data.description: Discover your dream home in a nestled part of Hollywood! This remodeled 3BR, 1BA Single Family Home is a haven of modern living. With a new roof, high impact windows, and recently remodeled bathroom, the home radiates comfort and sophistication. The spacious backyard, set in a quiet cul-de-sac with no association, features an additional outdoor storage shed and ample space to build a pool. Additional features include a new concrete driveway, installed EV charging station, and a recently replaced HVAC system.     Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to make this your forever home!
